node.text:
50 years ago today...August 19, 1969. Our Love, Honor and Respect shines as bright today, as it did back then, and will continue for years to come. 
Cpl. Dennis F. Shine Jr. was a son, brother, husband, father, uncle, cousin and friend. He is our American Hero. ❤️🇺🇸💙 #honorthefallen #dad #goldstarfamily #vietnam #neverforget #proudfamily #ourhero #army #101stairborne #vietnamveteransmemorial

@pwbrandcottage these were all pics on my phone. tagged the location, since most were taken there. 
I’ll need to remember this the next time I visit. 💜
If you are still there please visit Marshall Robertson down a few rows/same panel
